examples.en: This hobby occupies all of my free time.
Football occupies most of my leisure time.
The building occupies an entire city block.
He occupies the house without paying any rent.
Their house occupies a beautiful spot next to the ocean.
She occupies the house that her grandfather built 50 years ago.
The department occupies an office just a mile from the White House.
We have seen a Chinese map of the world, in which the Celestial country occupies the entire space.
